<%- include("./partials/header.ejs"); %>
	<!-- Below component to blur background while leaderboard is open -->
	<div id="background-blur-outer">

	</div>
	<h1 id="rulesheading">Rules</h1>
	<div id="rulesdiv">
		<div id="boxdiv">
			<ul id="rulesul">
				<li class="rulesli">
					<i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>
					Number of questions are limited! Solve all the questions as quickly as possible!
				</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>There would be N questions and you can proceed to the next question only after
					answering one question right and so on.</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>Answers will always be lower-case, alphanumeric and will contain no spaces. Special
					characters are not allowed. If your answer is "Hello world 2" then you have to submit "helloworld2"
				</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>Brute Forcing the solution using software is not an option. Your IP will be blocked
					if found doing so.</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>This is an individual event. Only single participation is allowed.</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>Team play, answer sharing, hint sharing and collaborating with other competitors in
					general is not allowed and any such evidence can lead to disqualification.</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>Beware of the spelling you enter, we do not autocorrect.</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>Every clue in the question is important.</li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>One person can play on only one account. If found playing with multiple accounts,
					the person will be disqualified automatically. </li>
				<hr class="rulesul-hr">
				<li class="rulesli"><i class="fa fa-play fa-solid rules-bullet"></i>In case of any dispute, the decision of the society will be final and binding.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	</div>

